        protected <G extends org.gradoop.common.model.api.entities.GraphHead,V extends org.gradoop.common.model.api.entities.Vertex,E extends org.gradoop.common.model.api.entities.Edge> org.gradoop.temporal.model.impl.TemporalGraph toTemporalGraph(org.gradoop.flink.model.api.epgm.BaseGraph<G,V,E,?,?> graph,

        Convert a graph to a TemporalGraph and set temporal attributes using TimeIntervalExtractor functions.
        Type Parameters:
        G - The graph head type.
        V - The vertex type.
        E - The edge type.
        Parameters:
        graph - The graph.
        graphHeadTimeExtractor - The function used to extract temporal attributes for graph heads.
        vertexTimeExtractor - The function used to extract temporal attributes for vertices.
        edgeTimeExtractor - The function used to extract temporal attributes for edges.
        Returns:
        A temporal graph with temporal attributes extracted from the original graph.
